HEADWORD: mierkat
<hw>mierkat</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A South African
mongooselike viverrine (<spn>Suricata suricata</spn>) having a lemurlike
face and only four toes; called also <altname>suricate</altname>.</def>
<altsp>[Also spelled <asp>meerkat</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> meerkat.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

